name: Angularjsanalyse
body:
### Welcome to Angularjs Analyse Tool.
This software was developed to understand Angularjs project quickly. The programm looks for the key words and display them in a tree.  

The Setup for Windows can found on
[setup windows](https://github.com/rweinzierl1/AngularjsAnalyse/blob/master/innoSetup/Output/setup.exe)


The executable for Linux can found on
[setup linux](https://github.com/rweinzierl1/AngularjsAnalyse/blob/master/linux32/AngularAnalyse)


Then click on Raw version for Download

***

### Featurelist

Find Angularjs key words (Modules, Directives ...)
Qick search in project files
Nice Editor with preview 
Intelligence 

A Video (German Version)
[Video](http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KHvFFfKyvrw)



### Support or Contact
if you had trouble please send a mail to rweinzierl1 at googlemail.com
